{"tid":1263174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【回帶西】2014 G20奧巴馬公開支持香港雨傘運動；習：香港事務是中國內政","createTime":"2019-06-28T04:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T06:26:58.000Z","uid":23707,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"18e1b4aa0c3728c785a17abd1cafe9b074602019","tid":1263174,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1158244\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1158244&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2Fewiyebaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=2d2d7388\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1158244&h=b6f44a53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1158244</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統歐巴馬出席20國領導人峰會（G20）時，提及香港爭取真普選的「雨傘革命」，他認為，香港人是在爭取「普世權利」，美國會支持任何國家追求民主。<br />\n<br />\n歐巴馬在澳洲一所當地大學發表演講時，表示支持香港的佔中「雨傘革命」，歐巴馬認為，這是一場「支持民主」的抗議行動，香港人是在為普世權利發聲。<br />\n<br />\n不過中國國家主席習近平曾對歐巴馬表示，香港事務是中國內政，因此外界預估，歐巴馬此番言論將會觸動中國敏感神經。"},{"pid":"300553832f3664704cdd6cc3264ae80fe85f0278","tid":1263174,"uid":212246,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"2014年新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b288a174755016e39524dd6c79c2f047afbbed","tid":1263174,"uid":23707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"300553832f3664704cdd6cc3264ae80fe85f0278","tid":1263174,"uid":212246,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"2014年新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:26:58.000Z","msg":"咪寫撚明囉"}]}